com.aionemu.gameserver.model.account
Class Account

java.lang.Object
  com.aionemu.gameserver.model.account.Account
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<PlayerAccountData>
public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<PlayerAccountData>

This class represents game account and is holding such informations as:

  • account id
  • account name
  • account time info
  • a list of PlayerAccountData objects each of which keeping information about player that must be available on character selection screen.
